24:51.000 --> 24:53.000
Hi!

25:04.000 --> 25:06.000
- Hi.
- Hi.

25:07.000 --> 25:10.000
Risto, have you got the key?

25:10.035 --> 25:11.517
The little one, here.

25:11.552 --> 25:13.000
Come through here.

25:13.035 --> 25:14.517
Michael...

25:14.552 --> 25:15.965
That's good!

25:16.000 --> 25:18.965
There's a little
one. Move him to the front.

