- You should wear them.
- I quite like them.

25:30.035 --> 25:32.517
Everyone else is wearing them.

25:32.552 --> 25:34.965
That RTL driver was saved by his.

25:35.000 --> 25:39.000
- Wear them on petrol runs.
- Mm, all right.

25:39.035 --> 25:42.517
I don't know if we
can get insured without them.

25:42.552 --> 25:45.776
- I know you don't like them...
- Shh! Listen.

25:45.811 --> 25:49.000
'I buried these children
in the garden... '

25:49.035 --> 25:50.965
Wonder if she's insured (!)

25:51.000 --> 25:53.965
'.. everyone can see we are dying.

25:54.000 --> 25:59.000
'So I will not put them away,
out of sight.

25:59.035 --> 26:02.000
'Everyone must know we are dying.

26:03.000 --> 26:04.965
'So... tell them.

26:05.000 --> 26:08.000
'Keep on telling them
until they will move us. '

26:16.000 --> 26:19.965
'If it is possible
to treat children there,

26:20.000 --> 26:24.000
'near to their families, with
people who speak their language

26:24.035 --> 26:26.000
'and in relatively
familiar surroundings,

26:26.035 --> 26:28.965
'then that is the best way. '

