'Emira has been here
since she was a baby.

27:42.000 --> 27:47.000
'Now she's so frightened,
she can't sleep at night. '

27:52.000 --> 27:55.000
'Sead's mother was killed
in a mortar attack.

28:01.000 --> 28:04.000
'Zaned is from a village
near Sarajevo.

28:04.035 --> 28:05.965
'His father and two older brothers

28:06.000 --> 28:09.000
'were taken prisoner
by Serb irregulars,

28:09.005 --> 28:09.995
'the feared Chetniks.

28:10.000 --> 28:14.000
'His mother was shot by a sniper
whilst queuing for water. '

28:18.000 --> 28:20.000
Got a permission letter
from Radovan Karadjic

28:20.035 --> 28:23.017
so we can get behind Serb lines.

28:23.052 --> 28:25.965
It can't
be much of a story, then.

28:26.000 --> 28:31.000
Anyway, we've got a story.
50 kids who could be blown up

28:31.035 --> 28:33.000
and nobody's paying any attention.

28:33.005 --> 28:33.995
We've done that story.

28:34.000 --> 28:36.965
We've STARTED that story.
They're still there.

28:37.000 --> 28:41.000
As long as the UN's here
I'll keep those kids on screen.

28:41.035 --> 28:42.965
Same message - "Get me out. "

28:43.000 --> 28:45.965
That's not news. That's a campaign.

28:46.000 --> 28:50.000
I don't care.
I'm gonna get those kids out.

28:50.005 --> 28:50.995
What's the problem?

28:51.000 --> 28:55.000
Big guns, little children,
evil men - great television.

28:55.035 --> 28:57.965
- If it works.
- Good night.

28:58.000 --> 29:01.000
- Won't listen, will he?
- Oh, dear!

29:04.000 --> 29:05.965
Since the war,

29:06.000 --> 29:08.000
the orphanage has taken in
not only babies

29:08.035 --> 29:09.965
but also older children,

29:10.000 --> 29:13.000
many of whom have witnessed
terrible events

29:13.035 --> 29:16.000
as well as being separated
from their families.

